lemma sets_distinct6: "(s::int) < g \<Longrightarrow> {(a::int, b::int). g < a} \<noteq> {(a::int, b::int). a = s}"
proof -
assume "s < g"
thus "{(a, b). g < a} \<noteq> {(a, b). a = s}"
by force
qed
